data.description: Take A Look At This Outstanding, Meticulously Maintained, Almost Single Story Residence! Only The Game Room & 1 Bath Are Up. All 4 Bedrooms Down (3 Way Split), Also A Private Study With Double French Doors. The Master Bedroom And The Front Guest Room Both Have Ensuite Baths. The Other Secondary Bedrooms Share A Jack & Jill Bath. Large Living Area With Floor To Ceiling Austin Stone Fireplace. Extensive, Hardwood & Ceramic Tile Flooring Almost Throughout. The Game-Media-Play Room Offers Ample Storage, Has A Wet-Bar (Fridge Remains) And A Half Bath. Ideal For Kids Sleep Overs, Or A More Adult Use When Equipped With Pool Table & Big Screen TV. The Outdoors Can Be Enjoyed On The Spacious, Covered Patio (Ceiling Fan & Mounted TV) Overlooking The Heated Pool & Spa, & Additional Water Features (my favorite is the Dragon Egg) Much $$ Went Into Designing & Implementing This Lovely Back Yard Oasis! Extensive Land & Hardscaping With Large Urns & Architectural Stones. New Roof 06-2023
